name: Abrasive Catalyst
description:
Adds quality that enhances Attack modifiers on a ring, amulet or belt
Replaces other quality types
helpText: Right click this item then left click a ring, amulet or belt to apply it. Has greater effect on lower item level, non-unique jewellery. The maximum quality is 20%.
